reviews: For the price, can't beat it. The double/twin package is an excellent deal for the price.

review_title: Very sensitive to other electrical interference & position
reviews: Very sensitive to other electrical interference & position. Even walking by it could cause some glitches. The powered on DVD player nearby would completely eliminate channel reception. Placement is important. Having said that, once it was in a stable location, and no interference, reception was very good.
Not bad for the price. But the audio is terrible and you can’t adjust the volume of the speaker. It’s very loud.
Extremely comfortable. Wears well, not too wide. But You’re forced to turn up the hat so much that it doesn’t look right, looks odd with so much folded up. Doesn’t need to be made so long.
Even though their main clients may be medical professionals, the documentation could include a layman’s description of what the results tell you (instead of going to the Internet).
Too big for the average finger.
Sufficient to play the songs from the show.
Thinner gauge metal. The screws supplied were sufficient to mount the SSD itself, but not big enough to mount the bracket itself. Did the job.
So far so good. Some have a rougher edge than others, which is fine because it's even more effective in its massage purpose.

Very good quality product. Protects speaker well and the case is perfect for the size and weight of the speaker and charger. It got a 4 only because the protective rubber sleeve that goes around the speaker does not have an opening to access the AUX jack.
